definition: to annihilate/abbr. for 殲擊機|歼击机, fighter plane

sentences.english: In addition to the luxury vehicles, the factory turned out engines for World War II fighter planes.
sentences.chinese: 除了豪華汽車，這座工廠還爲二戰生產殲擊機發動機。

sentences.english: The fighter planes quickly disengaged from the combat.
sentences.chinese: 殲擊機很快從戰鬥中撤出了。

sentences.english: This paper deals with a similarity-transformation method for obtaining engine design loading section.
sentences.chinese: 本文提出了獲得殲擊機發動機載荷剖面的相似轉換法。
